                   -}===-  Assassin Guild Help  -==={-
-------------------========] Help List Three [========-----------------------
Command:            Cost:   Description:
DECEPTION:
disguise <who>      50      Disguise yourself as something else.
sneak <who>         75      Teleport silently to player.
stalk <who>         15      Silently follow who.
fear <who>          5       Frighten player out of room.
: <what>                    Emote. Wow!
bug <who>           15      Bug someone.
bugroom <who>|here  15      Bug the room of who or here.

UTILITY COMMANDS:
adjust_myself               Reset your license.
contract a b                Contract with a to assassinate b.
guildhome [church]          Start out in guild hall or church if specified.
